{
  "stem": "26731.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were two newspapers, one local and one more for Germany as such.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I actually didn't read them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Occasionally, I read the local newspaper, but I-- frankly, only once in a while.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I heard-- heard people talk, yes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Uh-- try to, uh, to go to various countries, to China, Brazil, Uruguay, and so on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You knew that people try to get out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I really don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was too young to actually, uh, go and to read it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the parades was always there, but not before beginning of the war.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember close to 1939, just before the war, you could see quite a bit of, uh, trains, with tanks, and so on.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And actually it was quite obvious that something would happen, you see.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't know what.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But, uh, you could see it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the beginning, uh, of the actual war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, it was quite something.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In fact, all the signs disappeared.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Everything.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You could sit everywhere.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You could do anything you wanted.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was being told, and probably I believe it, that people were instructed, be very careful.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "No anti-Semitic remark.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Be very polite to everyone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because you didn't know, somebody might look Jewish, but, uh, who knows?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Was from Italy or you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And, uh, I remember they got brand new, um, elevated trains.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And, uh, everything was absolutely-- streets were clean.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Absolutely everything was just organized beautiful.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And you could go everywhere.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At that time already, um, they didn't like to see you in certain movies- movie theaters and, uh, opera houses.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It wasn't officially, that came a little bit later, but, uh, probably some people didn't.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the general population was not already anti-Semitic, but already enough people were looking for troubles.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
